   <q>
      <bibl>1. PETER. 3.15.16.</bibl>
      <p>Sanctifye the Lorde God in your heartes, and be ready alwayes to geue an aunswere to euery man that asketh you a reason of the hope that is in you.</p>
      <p>And that with meekenesse and reacrence, hauing a good conscience, that when they speake euill of you as of euill dooers, they may be ashamed which blame your good conuersation in Christe.</p>
   </q>
